Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: pycanvass
Version: 0.0.2.5
Summary: Python API for Cyber Attack and Network Vulnerability Assessment Software for Smartgrid
Home-page: http://github.com/sayonsom/pycanvass
Author: Sayonsom Chanda
Author-email: sayon@ieee.org
License: GPL
Description: PyCanvass is an open source simulation software for computing resiliency of Smart Grid and power systems critical infrastructure.
        It has a unique resiliency computation engine, and it enables integration with other industry-standard power system simulation software like GridLAB-D, and Real-Time Digital Simulators.
        
        PyCanvass was developed by Sayonsom Chanda, at Washington State University - and is still maintained by him. If you have any questions, or find bugs - please email: sayon@ieee.org
        
        
